<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to CometJet!</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .email-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a00e0, #8e2de2);
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .message p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .highlight {
      color: #7f3fbf;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #7f3fbf;
      margin: 25px 0 15px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    
    .aircraft-list {
      background-color: #f9f5ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #7f3fbf;
    }
    
    .aircraft-item {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .note-box {
      background-color: #fff7e6;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffa940;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .action-section {
      background-color: #f0f5ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a00e0, #8e2de2);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 10px 5px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.4);
    }
    
    .platform-section {
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    .discord-section {
      background-color: #5865F2;
      color: white;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .discord-section a {
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .signature {
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    a {
      color: #7f3fbf;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    
    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .important-note {
      color: #ff4d4f;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/L2ECQuk.png" alt="CometJet Logo" class="logo">
      <h1>Welcome to CometJet!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">
        <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message">
        <p>We are happy to inform you that you have been accepted as a pilot in CometJet. Congratulations! We are sure that we are leaving one of our aircraft in good hands.</p>
        
        <p>Your application you sent made a great impression on us. Your enthusiasm and passion for aviation are in line with our mission to provide the highest quality aviation services to our passengers.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="action-section">
        <p>To fully join CometJet crew, you must join our airline on the licensed platform. It allows you to organize, track and save all your flights.</p>
        
        <p>Before performing your first flight, please read the SOP (Standard Operating Procedures) and download the proxy for your aircraft, which you can find by clicking <a href="www.cs.downloads">HERE</a>.</p>
        
        <p>Do you need training? Don't worry! You can sign up for our official training <a href="#">HERE</a>. Our comprehensive programs are designed to ensure you gain the knowledge and experience necessary to fly for CometJet VA.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
          <a href="#" class="btn">Join Our Platform</a>
          <a href="www.cs.downloads" class="btn">Download SOP & Proxy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="section-title">For MSPs Players</div>
      
      <div class="platform-section">
        <p>For better performance, we recommend downloading the MSPs add-on. Katowice Pyrawnice Airport EPKT, due to the fact that this airport is a CometJet Hub airport, which means that you will be at this airport quite often.</p>
        
        <p>To download the add-on click <a href="#">HERE</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="discord-section">
        <h3>Join Our Community!</h3>
        <p>Join our Discord to have access to all the information and contact us if you have any questions.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn" style="background: #7289DA;">Join Discord Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/L2ECQuk.png" alt="CometJet Logo" width="80"></p>
      <p class="signature">KayoJayoKayo and Aviaced - CometJet VA CEOs</p>
      <p>CometJet Virtual Airlines | www.cometjet-va.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
